VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT (?i)\b(MD2|MD4|MD5|SHA1|SHA-1|DES|RC2|RC4|RC5)\b
WHEN EXPR MISSING:(?i)\b(SHA-256|SHA256|SHA-384|SHA384|SHA-512|SHA512|AES-GCM|AES256)\b
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects the usage of insecure cryptographic algorithms in Java code.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Insecure Cryptographic Algorithm.
